      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BARKLEY LANE (4) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by half a length at The Gardens in a handy 23.27 beating Alfie Unleashed. Jumping from the pinch draw but in form and has the ability. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Can measure up again. REMEMBER PAL (1) turned in a moderate performance last time when eighth at Q Lakeside over 352m behind Magic Mystery (23.15) in a PM. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Can measure up this time. AURORA BLAZE (2) is first up since finishing eighth (19.44) in a Maiden at this track over 300m three months ago. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. MOON BUTTER (7) placed last time at big odds - worth some thought.",
